ole events. How are we going to capture the attention of the 9 million peop=
le who watched the gold medal game at the Olympics? <br/><br/><b>You also h=
ave expansion on the horizon.</b><br/><br/>It will help in the process of s=
elling Team 16, which is going to enter the league in 2026. That would=E2=
=80=99ve been the year that our C.B.A. was expiring. You can imagine that a=
ny uncertainty around labor peace would be challenging for the entire leagu=
